how to build a maven project?

  steps:
   file-->new--other--maven--maven project-->next
  -->create simple project-->use default location-->
  --Group Id--Artifact ID--Finish.
  Then update propertise file if needed
  <properties>
    <maven.compiler.target>17</maven.compiler.target>
    <maven.compiler.source>17</maven.compiler.source>
   </properties>
   
   Why do I need to update maven Java version?
     by default maven will build java 1.5 or 1.7
     your company will tell you what version to use
      1.5 is too old for maven
    
   
   what is pom.xml file?
     it is configuration file for the project
   
   what is artifactId ?
   is the project name
   
   what is the groupId ?
   package name
   
   HOW do you update your java in the maven
   <properties>
    <maven.compiler.target>17</maven.compiler.target>
    <maven.compiler.source>17</maven.compiler.source>
   </properties>
   
   why do we need maven project?